      </div>
      <a class="button" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdNIPea-ojKmIPihNgORXpzgzXO13yIB4L5qMN_mJhlIJYz6Q/viewform" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">google formで送ってみる</a>
      <div class="sub-inner">
        <h3>💌 メール・SNSでも募集中 💌</h3>
        <div class="sub-info">
          <a class="subtext" href=mailto:>peachoolong000@gmail.com</a>
